snippet.title: Elon Musk SPEAKS On Rumors About Being The Father of Amber Heard’s Baby
snippet.description:
Welcome back to our channel, Fabulously Famous. Today will be talking about Elon Musk SPEAKS On Rumors About Being Amber Heard's Baby's Father! But before we get started, subscribe to our channel, to never miss any updates... So without any further delay let’s get started quickly.

Well, this is the most unexpected news of 2021. Guess what? Amber Heard is a mother now, yes you heard it right! The Warner brothers' favorite star is a mother to a beautiful newborn girl. Wait, wait there's a lot to this story starting from the official baby announcement to finding out the father of the baby, let me break this all down for you...

Starting with the good news first, Amber Heard officially shared a picture of herself with the baby lying on her stomach on her Official Instagram Handle. She wrote, "I am very happy to share this information with you. Four years ago, I decided I wanted to have a baby. I want to do it in my own words. Now appreciate how it is beneficial for us women to consider one of the most important aspects of our thinking in this way."
